name: Entity Unknown
description: - Alone in the dark I am weary of the silence in my mind. A growing unrest is materializing in the air around me as I meditate to the hum of my soul.- A Blender render which started from emotions of being lost and resulting in a visual representation that feels slightly warmer than my mind at the time of creation. Textures used captured from my own acrylic pour paintings.
